Package: archive
Title: Multi-format Archive and Compression support for R Connections.
Description: Bindings to 'libarchive' <http://www.libarchive.org> the
  Multi-format archive and compression library. Offers file connections for many
  archive formats including 'tar', 'ZIP', '7-zip', 'RAR', 'CAB' and compressions
  formats including 'gzip', 'bzip2', 'compress', 'lzma' and 'xz'.
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Jim", "Hester", email = "james.f.hester@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: Rcpp, tibble
Suggests: testthat,
    covr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
SystemRequirements: libarchive: libarchive-dev (deb), libarchive-devel (rpm), libarchive
  (homebrew), libarchive_dev (csw)
Remotes: jimhester/covr
URL: https://jimhester.github.io/archive/, https://github.com/jimhester/archive#readme
ByteCompile: true
